WEBVTT

00:00.640 --> 00:02.960
Don't trust and rely too much on your followers

00:03.480 --> 00:05.200
Don't become their puppet

00:05.680 --> 00:07.920
You and your elder brother are family

00:09.640 --> 00:10.640
This realm

00:10.720 --> 00:13.200
Will always belong to the Sikong family

00:14.280 --> 00:15.040
Your son understands

00:16.240 --> 00:17.000
Go

00:18.160 --> 00:18.760
Your son

00:19.680 --> 00:20.360
Takes leave

00:36.040 --> 00:36.920
Prince of Jin

00:39.680 --> 00:40.200
Miss Chen

00:42.000 --> 00:42.840
What a coincidence

00:43.280 --> 00:44.440
I'm here on my granduncle's orders

00:44.680 --> 00:46.120
To report to His Majesty

00:46.640 --> 00:47.600
I've discovered

00:47.880 --> 00:49.200
The trouble in Qing Province

00:49.640 --> 00:51.440
Was someone deliberately framing Prince of Ning

00:52.960 --> 00:54.000
Could it be Miss Chen

00:54.400 --> 00:55.600
Has already found the mastermind?

00:56.240 --> 00:56.840
That's right

00:57.040 --> 00:58.480
Drag him over for Prince of Jin to see

01:01.120 --> 01:02.200
His name is Guo Xuan

01:02.440 --> 01:03.920
Son of the Governor of Qing Province

01:04.600 --> 01:06.120
The canal project was obstructed

01:06.200 --> 01:07.160
And sparked rebellion

01:07.440 --> 01:09.000
Precisely because this man and his father

01:09.000 --> 01:10.400
Were manipulating behind the scenes

01:10.960 --> 01:11.680
The Chancellor

01:12.200 --> 01:14.000
Will submit a memorial tomorrow to impeach

01:15.760 --> 01:17.360
And thoroughly investigate the Guo family's crimes

01:18.400 --> 01:19.600
A provincial governor

01:19.640 --> 01:20.960
Just to take the blame

01:21.400 --> 01:23.360
The Chen family, to get elder brother out

01:23.560 --> 01:24.800
Has really gone all out

01:25.240 --> 01:26.640
How should I respond?
